data.description:
Beautiful 4 years new Duplex.  
Includes top of the line features. Fully appointed kitchens include; quartz countertops, spacious single bowl under mount sinks, Aristokraft  cabinets & stainless steel GE  appliances. Homes also feature; LED surface mounted lighting in the hallways and bedrooms, modern two panel interior doors & colonist trim, vinyl plank flooring in the kitchen, foyer, bathrooms & laundry upstairs laundry room, a garage door opener, 30 year architectural shingles & so much more, all of which are included with this beautiful home. 
Master bedroom has ceiling fan with large walk in closet and private attached full bathroom.  Large foyer entry. Beautiful kitchen with white cabinets,  quartz counter tops, and stainless steel appliances! Plus, superior Smart Home Automation. Remote access to the thermostat, a wireless touch entry, and a Ring video doorbell built right into the home!
Updated with top of the line screen door at main entrance with slide down storm to screen for easy switching. Overhead and wall storage installed in garage.
Extended patio with upgraded pavers. Front door can be opened with key or code lock.  Low association fees at only $110 a month.  Painted with modern gray colors. New Aprilaire installed on furnace.
Lincolnway Highschool.  Close to restaurants,  shopping and parks, I-80 and 355!
***Will pay buyers agent 2%***
data.whatILove:
Well kept duplex home with upgraded amenities that is almost new in a great neighborhood!  Low association fees at 110 a month so no worries about snow removal or mowing.  Great Lincolnway Highschool and close to highways!
Taxes approximately 8500  year
